Package edu.baylor.ecs.sw1.event

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EventBuilder
    EventBuilder is an interface for an object that builds an Event of some subtype, setting its necessary fields.
    EventVisitor
    This interface requires its implementations to implement a visit method taking an event.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Assignment
    Subclass of Event pertaining to most events
    AssignmentBuilder
    Implementation of EventBuilder that creates new Assignments
    Course
    Subclass of Event pertaining specifically to time spent in class
    Event
    Abstract Event class that holds data about events, and accepts some visitors
    EventCreationDialog
    This class displays a dialog that gets information for the creation of an event, and validates the info before returning the event.
    EventDisplayer
    This class displays a dialog with the event information.
    EventEditDialog
    This dialog displays an event's information and allows it to be edited.
    Quiz
    Subclass of Event pertaining specifically to quizzes, which is one of the ways that Canvas stores event info
    QuizBuilder
    Implementation of EventBuilder that creates new Quizzes
